altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 35
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 35
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v35 (released as a Pokémon Channel Bonus Disc in Japan) is a demo and video sampler disc of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Paper Mario: The Thousand-Year Door, Star Fox: Assault, and Pikmin 2. The disc also features videos of: Paper Mario: The Thousand-Year Door, Star Fox: Assault, Pikmin 2, The Legend of Zelda: Four Swords Adventures, Brain Age (DS), Nintendo GameCube, and an ESRB ratings video.
